OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill continue to bring showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, and a
OL,8,Fmixture of low cloud and fog leading
OL,9,Fto poor driving conditions,
OL,10,Fparticularly over the hills and
OL,11,Fmountains. Staying frost free under
OL,12,Fthe blanket of cloud.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,15,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,16,Fwill brighten a little later in the
OL,17,Feast with some hazy spells of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
